title: Around the NFC in 48 minutes!
itunes:title: Around the NFC in 48 minutes!
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – discuss every team in the NFC following the 2016 NFL Draft. Highlights include which quarterback will start for the Eagles, how much Jameis Winston will grow in his sophomore year and if anyone can challenge the Panthers in the NFC South. Plus, the heroes debate which team is the front runner in the loaded NFC.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
